title: FSX 747X World Airliners 5
description:
6HDT repaints for PMDG's one and only 'Queen of the Skies'. With a pixel per meter ratio of 171, these textures are not only four times as detailed as the repaints made by PMDG but also quite a bit more detailed than our MD-11 High Definition World Airliners.
